ISLAMABAD, Aug 3 (APP):President Asif Ali Zardari has summoned a session of the Senate, at the Parliament House, on Monday.
The president summoned a session of the upper house of parliament on August 5, at 5:00 p.m., under Article 54 (1) of the Constitution of Pakistan, President Secretariat Press Wing, on Saturday, said in a press release.
